snippet.title: AntiChamber: TRIPPY MIND GAME! (Mind-Bending Psychological Exploration)
snippet.description:
AntiChamber Website: http://www.antichamber-game.com/
Download on Steam: http://store.steampowered.com/app/219890/
Ratings are Appreciated! Feedback is Welcome!
Download the AntVenom Browser Add-on: http://bit.ly/W6F6j6

Website: http://www.AntVenom.com
Merchandise Store: http://antvenom.spreadshirt.com
Twitter: http://twitter.com/AntVenom
Facebook: http://tinyurl.com/AntVenomFB
Twitch.TV: http://twitch.tv/AntVenom

The music comes from the in-game Minecraft soundtrack. If you would like to listen without having Minecraft playing, you can download it here: http://c418.bandcamp.com/album/minecraft-volume-alpha

Outro Track by Approaching Nirvana
Evolve Album - Death of a King
Download the Album: http://bit.ly/T7lIiH
